                  = ( P @ Xaa ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xh )
                  = ( P @ Xhh ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xb )
                  = ( P @ Xcc ) ) )
             => ( ( P @ Xd )
               != ( P @ Xee ) ) )
            & ( ( ( ( P @ Xc )
                  = ( P @ Xcc ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xcc )
                  = ( P @ Xd ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xd )
                  = ( P @ Xdd ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xa )
                 != ( P @ Xbb ) ) )
             => ( ( P @ Xe )
               != ( P @ Xhh ) ) )
            & ( ( ( ( P @ Xa )
                  = ( P @ Xaa ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xd )
                  = ( P @ Xdd ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xb )
                 != ( P @ Xcc ) ) )
             => ( ( P @ Xe )
                = ( P @ Xhh ) ) )
            & ( ( ( ( P @ Xe )
                  = ( P @ Xee ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xh )
                  = ( P @ Xhh ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xc )
                  = ( P @ Xdd ) ) )
             => ( ( P @ Xa )
               != ( P @ Xbb ) ) )
            & ( ( ( ( P @ Xb )
                  = ( P @ Xbb ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xbb )
                  = ( P @ Xc ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xc )
                  = ( P @ Xcc ) )
                & ( ( P @ Xe )
                 != ( P @ Xhh ) ) )
             => ( ( P @ Xd )
                = ( P @ Xee ) ) ) )
         => ( ( ( P @ Xa )
             != ( P @ Xaa ) )
            | ( ( P @ Xb )
             != ( P @ Xbb ) )
            | ( ( P @ Xc )
             != ( P @ Xcc ) )
            | ( ( P @ Xd )
             != ( P @ Xdd ) )
            | ( ( P @ Xe )
             != ( P @ Xee ) )
            | ( ( P @ Xh )
             != ( P @ Xhh ) ) ) ) ) ).

